Find your next car on AutoTempest: https://vinwiki.com/r/autotempest
AutoTempest compiles listings from all the major listing sites in one search making it easier than ever to quickly find the car of your dreams.  

Today @Ed Bolian updates us on his search for McLaren F1 Chassis 039 that has been missing in Western Mexico for 16 years. The cars was owned by El Chapo's greatest drug runner.
